      "content": "but i really dont think i can make it to the doctor until tomorrow or the day after and it's not that much fluid. if i just use the antibiotic ointment and a warm soak tonight to draw the stuff out, wouldn't that help keep it from getting worse? i'm pretty sure i can handle it if i just keep it clean and treated.",
